<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        line-height: 1.8;
        background-color: #fafafa;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #333;
      }
      h3 {
        color: #ffffff;
        background-color: #333;
        padding: 10px;
      }
      p {
        color: #666;
      }
      a {
        color: #0066cc;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #777;
        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      }
      .footer p {
        font-size: 0.8em;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div style="text-align: left">
        <div style="padding-bottom: 20px">
          <img
            src="https://halcredit.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/halcredit-black.png"
            alt="Company"
            style="width: 120px"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2>Welcome and Next Steps</h2>
      <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for your interest in investing with us.</p>

      <p>
        These are the steps that we need to take to complete your investment in
        this round
      </p>

      <h3>Step 1: Complete our KYC</h3>
      <p>Please use the link below to complete the identity confirmation.</p>

      <p>
        <a href=<%= verificationLink %>>Know-Your-Customer (KYC) Form</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        This is a requirement by law as a potential shareholder of a private
        company.
      </p>

      <h3>Step 2: Transfer Instructions</h3>
      <p>
        Once the KYC process has been confirmed, you will receive an email from
        us with the bank details and instructions for the transfer. Please note
        that all transfers have to be made into the companyâ€™s USD account. If
        you need assistance with transferring your funds, kindly reach out to
        the team. We will provide all the necessary details for all
        international transfers.
      </p>

      <h3>Step 3: Forward Transfer Receipt</h3>
      <p>
        Once your transfer has been made, kindly forward your transaction
        receipt or telex copy to this email: investor@halcredit.com or + 234
        7042915411 or +234 8029093009.
      </p>

      <p>
        We will send a confirmation receipt upon receiving your investment
        amount. Please allow 3 - 4 days for us to confirm all international
        transfers.
      </p>

      <h3>Step 4: Investment Receipt</h3>
      <p>
        We will forward an investment receipt to you to confirm your investment
        in this round.
      </p>

      <h3>Step 5: Sign SAFE Contract</h3>
      <p>
        We will forward the SAFE contract to your email. Your name, passport
        number and signature will be on this contract and will be used to
        convert your investment in our next priced round at the terms that have
        been stipulated on the investment page. And this completes your
        investment in the Halcredit Pre-seed Private Angel Round 2023.
      </p>

      <p>Best Regards,</p>
      <p>Halcredit Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
         <p>Unsubscribe</p>
        <p>invest@halcredit.com</p>
        <p>+ 234 7042915411 or +234 8029093009</p>
        <p>https://www.halcredit.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
